Email Application

*************************************************

Scenario :You are an IT Support Administration Specialist and 
are charged with task creating email account of new Hires
Your Application Should do the following 
1.Genrate an email with following syntax firstname.lastname@department.company.com
2.Determine the Departments(Sales,Devlopment,Accounting)if none leave blank
3.Genrate the Random string for password 
4.Have Set Methods to Change the Password,Set the Mail Box Capacity and define alternate Mail Address 
5.Have get methods to display name,email,mailbox capacity
 